ISO_Left_Tab 0xf shift
q 0x10 addupper
d 0x11 addupper
r 0x12 addupper
w 0x13 addupper
b 0x14 addupper
j 0x15 addupper
f 0x16 addupper
u 0x17 addupper
p 0x18 addupper
p 0x19 addupper

